#

Korean BBQ Beef Tacos

$15.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Protein-richGluten-free

Tags:

Asian FusionStreet FoodCasual Dining

Description

Savory Korean BBQ beef served in soft corn tortillas with fresh toppings.

Ingredients

  • Flank steak: 1 lb
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Brown sugar: 2 tbsp
  • Sesame oil: 1 tbsp
  • Corn tortillas: 8
  • Cabbage (shredded): 1 cup
  • Carrots (shredded): 1/2 cup
  • Green onions (sliced): 1/4 cup
  • Sriracha sauce: to taste
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tbsp
